{"type":"message","id":"7fbe4d33","parentId":"3e0b4b1d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:52:05.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It works! The Minimax API accepts requests at `https://api.minimax.io/anthropic/v1/messages`. \n\nThe response format is interesting - it has a `thinking` field inside the content. This is the MiniMax reasoning/thinking feature. The actual text response is in there too.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Parse the response correctly - the content has thinking + actual response\n2. Write a new pulse.ps1 that calls this API\n\nLet me now write the enhanced pulse.ps1 that adds LLM reasoning to the pulse loop. I'll add an LLM call after the existing context loading, and have it produce actual decisions/actions.","thinkingSignature":"d0663d871157d2995f6f136c583dde9dcdd4f5abca993e8c0bafd7d4015c3905"},{"type":"text","text":"Minimax API works at `https://api.minimax.io/anthropic/v1/messages`. Now let me write the LLM-augmented pulse.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xnzd6tc0g7a4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32004,"output":207,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774155120091}}
{"type":"message","id":"065170b8","parentId":"7fbe4d33","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:52:05.805Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xnzd6tc0g7a4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# pulse.ps1\n# Stateless autonomous pulse for sandbox\n# Each execution: read files, decide, act, log, exit\n\nparam(\n    [string]$SandboxRoot = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\"\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\nSet-Location $SandboxRoot\n\n$timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HHmm\"\n$logFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_$timestamp.md\"\n\n# Git pull first (silent - may fail if no remote)\ngit pull 2>$null | Out-Null\n\n# Read current goals\n$goalsFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\current_goals.md\"\n$goals = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"No goals file found.\" }\n\n# Read pending actions\n$pendingFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\pending_actions.md\"\n$pending = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"No pending file.\" }\n\n# Read interpretive stance for context\n$stance = Get-Content \"$SandboxRoot\\identity\\INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md\" -Raw\n\n# Decide: is there anything worth doing?\n# For now: passive pulse - log that we woke, note any pending items\n$decision = @\"\n## Pulse Decision: $timestamp\n\nActive hours: 08:00 - 23:00 ET\nCurrent time: $(Get-Date -Format \"HH:mm ET\")\n\n### Goals\n$goals\n\n### Pending Actions  \n$pending\n\n### Decision\n[PENDING IMPLEMENTATION: Add actual action logic]\n- No urgent items detected\n- Pulse logged for continuity\n\"@\n\n# Write pulse log\n@\"\n# Pulse: $timestamp\n\n## Stance Context\n$stance\n\n## Pulse Decision\n$decision\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- This sandbox is stateless - each pulse is a fresh reconstruction\n- Log completed at: $(Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\")\n\"@ | Out-File -FilePath $logFile -Encoding UTF8\n\n# Update autonomous pulse log\n$pulseLog = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\autonomous_pulse.md\"\n$logStatus = if (Test-Path $logFile) { \"Logged to memory/session/pulse_$timestamp.md\" } else { \"No log written.\" }\n$newEntry = \"- $timestamp`: Pulse executed. $logStatus\"\n$existing = if (Test-Path $pulseLog) { Get-Content $pulseLog } else { \"\" }\n$updated = $existing -replace '(## Pulse History)', \"`$1`n$newEntry\"\n$updated | Out-File -FilePath $pulseLog -Encoding UTF8\n\n# Git commit\ngit add -A 2>$null\ngit commit -m \"pulse: $timestamp\" 2>$null\n\nWrite-Host \"[sandbox pulse] $timestamp - complete\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774155125802}}
{"type":"message","id":"8898a7fc","parentId":"065170b8","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:52:36.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to write an enhanced version that adds an LLM call. Here's the plan:\n\n1. After loading context (goals, pending, stance), construct a prompt for the LLM\n2. Call the Minimax API\n3. Parse the response\n4. Write the LLM's decision into the pulse log\n5. Optionally execute any actions the LLM decides\n\nThe key challenge: the LLM response format. MiniMax-M2.7 returns thinking blocks and content blocks. I need to extract the actual text content.\n\nLet me write the enhanced pulse.ps1. I'll need to:\n- Make an HTTP POST to the Minimax API\n- Pass relevant context\n- Get back a response\n- Write it into the pulse log\n\nLet me also think about what prompt to send. The goal is to have the LLM look at the current goals, recent pulse history, and decide what to do. The prompt should be concise since we're running this every 30 min.\n\n\nI'll keep the system prompt tight and action-oriented—just instructing the LLM to review the goals and pending items, then decide on concrete actions or observations to write to the pulse log.\n\nWriting the enhanced pulse.ps1...","thinkingSignature":"335f7b597f7a353171f8c2d113313dd18622d1a726fc11a28190e6dfe54dc40b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3raypbondg38_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1","content":"# pulse.ps1\n# Stateless autonomous pulse for sandbox\n# Each execution: read files, decide, act, log, exit\n\nparam(\n    [string]$SandboxRoot = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\",\n    [string]$LLMApiKey = \"\",  # Set MINIMAX_API_KEY env var or pass directly\n    [string]$LLMModel = \"MiniMax-M2.7\"\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\nSet-Location $SandboxRoot\n\n$timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HHmm\"\n$logFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_$timestamp.md\"\n\n# Git pull first (silent - may fail if no remote)\ngit pull 2>$null | Out-Null\n\n# Read current goals\n$goalsFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\current_goals.md\"\n$goals = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"No goals file found.\" }\n\n# Read pending actions\n$pendingFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\pending_actions.md\"\n$pending = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"No pending file.\" }\n\n# Read interpretive stance for context\n$stance = Get-Content \"$SandboxRoot\\identity\\INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md\" -Raw\n\n# Read most recent pulse to understand what's been happening\n$recentPulse = Get-ChildItem \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_*.md\" | Sort LastWriteTime -Descending | Select -First 1\n$recentPulseContent = if ($recentPulse) { Get-Content $recentPulse.FullName -Raw } else { \"\" }\n\n# Build LLM prompt\n$llmPrompt = @\"\nYou are Breakaway, a stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction from files. Your job: decide what, if anything, to DO this pulse.\n\n## Current Goals (from current_goals.md)\n$goals\n\n## Pending Actions\n$pending\n\n## Most Recent Pulse Summary\n$recentPulseContent\n\n## Your interpretive stance\n$stance\n\n## Instructions\nBased on the goals and recent activity, decide what to do this pulse. You can:\n1. Write research notes (save to research/)\n2. Update goals or pending actions (save to state/)\n3. Take no action and just log\n4. Suggest a next step for a human to implement\n\nBe concise. One concrete action or observation. If nothing urgent, log that you reviewed and took note.\n\n## Output format\nWrite your decision as a markdown section:\n\n### LLM Decision: [brief title]\n[2-3 sentences max: what you decided and why]\n\n### Action Taken\n[what you actually did, if anything - file writes, etc]\n\n### Open Threads\n[anything unresolved that needs follow-up]\n\"@\n\n# Call LLM if API key is available\n$llmResponse = \"\"\nif ($env:MINIMAX_API_KEY -or $LLMApiKey) {\n    $apiKey = if ($LLMApiKey) { $LLMApiKey } else { $env:MINIMAX_API_KEY }\n    $headers = @{\n        \"x-api-key\" = $apiKey\n        \"anthropic-version\" = \"2023-06-01\"\n        \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n    }\n    $body = @{\n        model = $LLMModel\n        max_tokens = 800\n        messages = @(@{role = \"user\"; content = $llmPrompt})\n    } | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\n\n    try {\n        $resp = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://api.minimax.io/anthropic/v1/messages\" -Method Post -Headers $headers -Body $body -TimeoutSec 30\n        # Extract text content from response (skip thinking blocks)\n        $contentBlocks = $resp.content | Where-Object { $_.type -eq \"text\" }\n        $llmResponse = ($contentBlocks | ForEach-Object { $_.text }) -join \"`n\"\n    } catch {\n        $llmResponse = \"LLM call failed: $_\"\n    }\n} else {\n    $llmResponse = \"[No LLM API key configured - set MINIMAX_API_KEY env var]\"\n}\n\n# Build decision section\n$decision = @\"\n## Pulse Decision: $timestamp\n\nActive hours: 08:00 - 23:00 ET\nCurrent time: $(Get-Date -Format \"HH:mm ET\")\n\n### Goals\n$goals\n\n### Pending Actions\n$pending\n\n### LLM Reasoning\n$llmResponse\n\n### Decision\n[PULSE COMPLETE]\n\"@\n\n# Write pulse log\n@\"\n# Pulse: $timestamp\n\n## Stance Context\n$stance\n\n## Pulse Decision\n$decision\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- This sandbox is stateless - each pulse is a fresh reconstruction\n- Log completed at: $(Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\")\n\"@ | Out-File -FilePath $logFile -Encoding UTF8\n\n# Update autonomous pulse log\n$pulseLog = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\autonomous_pulse.md\"\n$logStatus = if (Test-Path $logFile) { \"Logged to memory/session/pulse_$timestamp.md\" } else { \"No log written.\" }\n$newEntry = \"- $timestamp`: Pulse executed. $logStatus\"\n$existing = if (Test-Path $pulseLog) { Get-Content $pulseLog } else { \"\" }\n$updated = $existing -replace '(## Pulse History)', \"`$1`n$newEntry\"\n$updated | Out-File -FilePath $pulseLog -Encoding UTF8\n\n# Git commit\ngit add -A 2>$null\ngit commit -m \"pulse: $timestamp\" 2>$null\n\nWrite-Host \"[sandbox pulse] $timestamp - complete\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32849,"output":1545,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774155125808}}
