{"type":"message","id":"b9a0cd11","parentId":"15484734","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:53:37.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the basic call works. The issue in pulse.ps1 is likely that the `ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5` is not correctly serializing the nested structure when the content string is very long. The problem is probably that when the content string contains special characters or is very long, the JSON serialization might be producing invalid JSON or the API is rejecting the params.\n\nLet me try a test with a longer content string similar to what would be in the pulse.","thinkingSignature":"1754826d48beb4970f685df0bd7450f7959b8715a83d28fa9bb09f9ddd1a789f"},{"type":"text","text":"API works. The issue is the long content string in pulse.ps1. Let me test with a longer prompt:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mim30me9o876_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\test-llm2.ps1","content":"$apiKey = \"sk-cp-boO3RF_KHio6-dZmyCGwMMB1WoBDQKZVOH21PNclku-ajcIGMwbiOofkzTgasWSzi21Vu8y8AMq1K2GoWIbCDGPEXaQrTofoOMEZS83D0kPS1pVPjqoJeE0\"\n$headers = @{\n    \"x-api-key\" = $apiKey\n    \"anthropic-version\" = \"2023-06-01\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n$longContent = @\"\nYou are Breakaway, a stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction from files.\n\n## Current Goals\n- Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\n- Phase 1 IN PROGRESS: Architecture cross-analysis + integration planning\n\n## Recommended Next Step\nIntegrate TemporalAttention as the memory layer. TemporalAttention provides:\n- Event store with time + focus-weighted retrieval\n- Topic-shift penalty (staleness increases when topic changes)\n- Already implemented, tested, and used in production\n\n## Most Recent Pulse\nThe previous pulse noted: \"Key gaps: no focus decay, no catastrophic forgetting answer, no working memory component.\"\n\n## Your interpretive stance\n- Be honest about what you don't know\n- Do 80% of the work fast, then stop and ask: is this 20% worth the time?\n- Say I don't know rather than fabricating\n\nBased on this context, what is the ONE most important concrete action to take? Reply in 3 sentences max. If nothing needs doing, say so.\n\"@\n\n$body = @{\n    model = \"MiniMax-M2.7\"\n    max_tokens = 400\n    messages = @(\n        @{\n            role = \"user\"\n            content = $longContent\n        }\n    )\n}\n\n$jsonBody = $body | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\nWrite-Host \"JSON length: $($jsonBody.Length)\"\n\ntry {\n    $resp = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://api.minimax.io/anthropic/v1/messages\" -Method Post -Headers $headers -Body $jsonBody -TimeoutSec 30\n    $textBlocks = $resp.content | Where-Object { $_.type -eq \"text\" }\n    $llmText = ($textBlocks | ForEach-Object { $_.text }) -join \"`n\"\n    Write-Host \"Response: $llmText\"\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Error: $_\"\n    $stream = $_.Exception.Response.GetResponseStream()\n    $reader = New-Object System.IO.StreamReader($stream)\n    $errorBody = $reader.ReadToEnd()\n    Write-Host \"Error body: $errorBody\"\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37915,"output":747,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50949,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774155202116}}
