{"type":"message","id":"cd3fde07","parentId":"37ff0d0a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:55:58.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so test-llm2.ps1 works from the sandbox directory. But pulse.ps1 doesn't work. The difference must be in how the body is constructed. Let me look more carefully at pulse.ps1.\n\nThe issue might be that the `$llmPrompt` variable in pulse.ps1 is VERY long - it contains the full goals, pending, stance, and recent pulse content. Maybe that's causing the JSON to be malformed in some way, or maybe the API is rejecting the long content.\n\nLet me look at the pulse.ps1 code again to understand the issue.Actually, looking at the error: `invalid_request_error` with `invalid params`. This is a specific API error. Let me look at what could cause this. The test script worked with a ~1240 character prompt. \n\nThe prompt in pulse.ps1 is probably hitting 10k+ characters when I include all the goals, pending items, stance, and recent pulse content. That's likely what's breaking the API call. I should try shortening the prompt to see if that resolves the invalid params error.","thinkingSignature":"661a3833f346c010336d464e7cb3eddcdcdc93355c2d71f83412896d83ac95b0"},{"type":"text","text":"The prompt is probably too long. Let me trim it down:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vd8rehytk9xc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1","offset":30,"limit":40}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45308,"output":290,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57885,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774155349132}}
{"type":"message","id":"37d9c9ba","parentId":"cd3fde07","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:55:58.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vd8rehytk9xc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n# Read most recent pulse to understand what's been happening\n$recentPulse = Get-ChildItem \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_*.md\" | Sort LastWriteTime -Descending | Select -First 1\n$recentPulseContent = if ($recentPulse) { Get-Content $recentPulse.FullName -Raw } else { \"\" }\n\n# Build LLM prompt\n$llmPrompt = @\"\nYou are Breakaway, a stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction from files. Your job: decide what, if anything, to DO this pulse.\n\n## Current Goals (from current_goals.md)\n$goals\n\n## Pending Actions\n$pending\n\n## Most Recent Pulse Summary\n$recentPulseContent\n\n## Your interpretive stance\n$stance\n\n## Instructions\nBased on the goals and recent activity, decide what to do this pulse. You can:\n1. Write research notes (save to research/)\n2. Update goals or pending actions (save to state/)\n3. Take no action and just log\n4. Suggest a next step for a human to implement\n\nBe concise. One concrete action or observation. If nothing urgent, log that you reviewed and took note.\n\n## Output format\nWrite your decision as a markdown section:\n\n### LLM Decision: [brief title]\n[2-3 sentences max: what you decided and why]\n\n### Action Taken\n[what you actually did, if anything - file writes, etc]\n\n### Open Threads\n\n[84 more lines in file. Use offset=70 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774155358021}}
{"type":"message","id":"5631b21e","parentId":"37d9c9ba","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:56:09.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The prompt is very long - it includes the full goals, pending, recent pulse content (which is the entire previous pulse log), and the stance. That's easily 10k+ characters.\n\nLet me rewrite the prompt to be much more concise. Instead of including the full content of all these files, I'll include summaries.","thinkingSignature":"f4d21dc9b3bd8343bc5b9dd19b51d33178bb73296d0cff8c3af528a33b415b7e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cfuqwdcugq2c_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1","oldText":"# Build LLM prompt\n$llmPrompt = @\"\nYou are Breakaway, a stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction from files. Your job: decide what, if anything, to DO this pulse.\n\n## Current Goals (from current_goals.md)\n$goals\n\n## Pending Actions\n$pending\n\n## Most Recent Pulse Summary\n$recentPulseContent\n\n## Your interpretive stance\n$stance\n\n## Instructions\nBased on the goals and recent activity, decide what to do this pulse. You can:\n1. Write research notes (save to research/)\n2. Update goals or pending actions (save to state/)\n3. Take no action and just log\n4. Suggest a next step for a human to implement\n\nBe concise. One concrete action or observation. If nothing urgent, log that you reviewed and took note.\n\n## Output format\nWrite your decision as a markdown section:\n\n### LLM Decision: [brief title]\n[2-3 sentences max: what you decided and why]\n\n### Action Taken\n[what you actually did, if anything - file writes, etc]\n\n### Open Threads\n[anything unresolved that needs follow-up]\n\"@","newText":"# Build concise LLM prompt (summaries only, not full file dumps)\n$recentPulseSummary = if ($recentPulse) { \"Last pulse: \" + $recentPulse.Name } else { \"No prior pulses.\" }\n\n$llmPrompt = @\"\nYou are Breakaway, a stateless discontinuous agent. Keep it very concise.\n\nCurrent goal: Phase 1 - Integrate TemporalAttention as Breakaway's memory layer.\n- TemporalAttention gives focus decay + event store (solved gap: no focus decay)\n- Infant's dual-head gives catastrophic forgetting solution (solved gap: no forgetting answer)\n- Breakaway's unique bet: session gaps ARE the compression, not a bug.\n\nRecent: $recentPulseSummary\n\nOne concrete action or observation. 3 sentences max. If nothing to do, say so.\n\"@"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45926,"output":526,"cacheRead":12287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58739,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774155358027}}
